message.body: What time you guys getting to philly tmw?

I can pick you up if you wanna come w us :)
My treat
Sure!!
We'll eat up your eggs fruit and toast. No need to buy anything

I have eggs and fruit and toast
What's your friends name?
Great!
Stacy. She went to Penn State. She's a history major and loves costuming.

Lol
